item.title: CVE-2023-39259|2024-08-12T14:12:53.802Z -- dell -- dell%20os%20recovery%20tool
item.description: Dell OS Recovery Tool, versions 2.2.4013, 2.3.7012.0, and 2.3.7515.0 contain an Improper Access Control Vulnerability. A local authenticated non-administrator user could potentially exploit this vulnerability, leading to the elevation of privilege on the system.
